dark.lib is a combination of `Cdark`'s libraries, made using dark.wrapper.

properties are prefixed with a single letter to indicate where they came from.
for example, `Nab` refers to the method `Nb` from the library `Na`. right now, the
included libraries are:

  `Na`: dark.arrays
  `Nc`: dark.corps
  `Ng`: dark.gc
  `No`: dark.objects
  `Ns`: dark.scriptors
  `Nt`: dark.text
  `Nu`: dark.upgrades
  `Nx`: dark.extras
